1.title: Together

episode of.title: The ABCs of Online Dating (TV Series 2014– )

1.plot: After a sudden breakup, Cara decides that she is going to take her love life into her own hands and join an online dating website. But she doesn't want to do it alone....so she candidly talks her two roommates, Ava and Bree, into joining the site with her. A great bonding experience or a recipe for disaster?

2.title: Business Contacts?

episode of.title: The ABCs of Online Dating (TV Series 2014– )

2.plot: The day after joining the dating website, always the overachiever, Bree, has a date with some guy named Steve...now if only her ever planning roommate Cara could just get a grip on her jealousy. And, a potential love interest appears at work...if only Bree could see it.

3.title: Mother Knows Best

episode of.title: The ABCs of Online Dating (TV Series 2014– )

3.plot: In the previous episode, we learn that Ava has also been asked out on a date! Problem: Cara hasn't been asked out yet so Cara can't know. It's for her own good, right? Well, Ava is about to see Karma's sick sense of humor when it Ava meets the "real" Michael...

4.title: Instagram vs. Photoshop

episode of.title: The ABCs of Online Dating (TV Series 2014– )

4.plot: Cara feels like she got dealt the wrong hand of cards today: her arch-nemesis, Alexandra, decided to use the company Cara works for to plan her wedding and Cara's dreamy date isn't so...dreamy... Plus, poor Bree meets the home wrecker who stole her now ex-boyfriend. Will the glass ever be "half-full" for these girls?

5.title: I Will Not Pay for Your...

episode of.title: The ABCs of Online Dating (TV Series 2014– )

5.plot: Coming off of seeing her ex-boyfriend with a new woman, Bree makes a decision to change her ways. Specifically, she's determined to be more spontaneous. But spontaneity doesn't necessarily work in her favor when she accepts a date with a staunch, opinionated vegetarian. Let's just wait and see how long this spontaneity will last.

6.title: Sean Connery Style

episode of.title: The ABCs of Online Dating (TV Series 2014– )

6.plot: Nothing ever seems to faze Ava, our resident artist of the ABCs. But she's in for two big surprises! One, her boss at the art gallery wants to show the gallery owner her art portfolio that's she's been working on for years! And two, she really hits it off with a dashingly handsome Scottish fellow. Things are finally starting to pan out for Ava...or are they?

7.title: Toy Sword Doc

episode of.title: The ABCs of Online Dating (TV Series 2014– )

7.plot: The catalyst for joining the online dating website FINALLY has a date with a very hunky doctor (who desires a "stepford wife" (or so Cara hopes)) but she has one large hurdle to overcome before she can go on her date: deal with her arch-nemesis, Alexandra. Can Cara keep it together as her patience wears thin?

8.title: Group Date

episode of.title: The ABCs of Online Dating (TV Series 2014– )

8.plot: In today's world, speed dating is OUT and group dates are IN! Cara, on her never ending pursuit of finding a man, is of course the first one to find out about the new feature on www.meetmrandmrsright.com - Group Date. This new feature allows for groups of friends to go on a group date all together. Cara looks at this from an efficiency perspective: kill three birds/guys with 1 stone/date. Ava is completely uninterested due to her ever growing interest in William. And Bree...is well...still "spontaneously" trying to win Brian back. May the awkward conversations begin...

9.plot: Bree has been trying to be more spontaneous and it had been working but now she's (accidentally) put it to the test. Being late for work is never fun, especially when your boss has it out for you. Literally. Also, her date is less than remarkable but DEFINITELY memorable.

imdb.title: The ABCs of Online Dating
akas: The ABCs of Online Dating (United States)
synopsis: Online dating is a multi-billion dollar industry that capitalizes on people who are all looking for the same thing: love. Now, each persons definition of love or the type of love they are seeking may vary but all in all, love is what people are searching for when doing online dating. With this series, we are bringing to the forefront the different types of people, situations, humor and cynicism that encompasses how many people feel about online dating both those who participate in online dating and those who have tried and it never worked out. This series revolves around the lives of three roommates, Ava, Bree and Cara (ABC) as they navigate the treacherous and unforgiving online dating world. The series opens with one of the roommates, Cara, being broken up with unexpectedly. As she is scrolling through the pictures of the two of them, she comes across an ad for an online dating website: meet Mr. and Mrs. Right. Cara decides to join, but doesn't want to do it alone. Cara candidly talks her two roommates, Ava and Bree, into joining the site as well. The series will follow the ladies as they go on a series of awful (and sadly non-fiction) bad online dates.
